    <h3>To Infinity and Beyond ♾️</h3>
    <p>From an African perspective we began by saying that Africa needs Ethereum. Then the narrative shifted to emphasize that Ethereum needs Africa. However, the truth is even more expansive: Ethereum needs the Global Majority. Across our regions, we share commonalities in culture, religion, and practices, while also celebrating our unique differences. Each of our communities is rooted in rich traditions that have endured for centuries, offering timeless wisdom and resilience.

      These methods and values have sustained us for generations, and they hold the power to guide us forward. Together, we possess a wealth of knowledge and playbooks to strengthen one another as we continue to engage in this infinite game—a game of growth, collaboration, and shared progress that has no end. The future is ours to build, and Ethereum is a tool that can help us cultivate it.</p>
    
